        <h3>What's New in 2026.06.04</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Measure my speed — Preferences → General times you typing then reading a short sentence, so Time Saved reflects your real typing/dictation speed instead of assumed defaults.</li>
          <li>Money Saved view — the Time Saved window has a new Time / $ toggle; set your hourly rate in Preferences to see your savings in your local currency.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
          All transcription happens 100% locally on your device.
        </p>
      ]]></description>
